msgctxt "1228_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san. Welcome."
msgstr "Hey, Kiryu-san. Welcome."

msgctxt "1240_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "It was you, wasn't it? You're the one that said those things to Matsuyama."
msgstr "It was you, wasn't it? You're the one that said those things to Matsuyama."

msgctxt "1252_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "He started getting all fired up after that. Oh man..."
msgstr "He started getting all fired up after that. Oh man..."

msgctxt "1264_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Should I have held back?"
msgstr "Heh. Should I have held back?"

msgctxt "1276_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Well, to be honest, I'm relieved you didn't..."
msgstr "Well, to be honest, I'm relieved you didn't..."

msgctxt "1288_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Eat up well, as my thanks! I'll still be charging you, of course!"
msgstr "Eat up well, as my thanks! I'll still be charging you, of course!"

msgctxt "1300_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Yeah, I might just do that."
msgstr "Heh. Yeah, I might just do that."

msgctxt "1324_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Thanks for coming by so often! The place's doing great because of you."
msgstr "Thanks for coming by so often! The place's doing great because of you."

msgctxt "1336_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Not exactly trying to pay you back, Akiyama-san, but if you ever get into a fight nearby, I'll be around to help you out!"
msgstr "Not exactly trying to pay you back, Akiyama-san, but if you ever get into a fight nearby, I'll be around to help you out!"

msgctxt "1360_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Welcome! What'll it be?"
msgstr "¡Bienvenido! ¿Qué va a pedir?"

msgctxt "1432_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Thanks! Please come again!"
msgstr "¡Gracias! ¡Por favor, vuelva pronto!"

msgctxt "1444_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "(I'm pretty full right now.)"
msgstr "(Estoy bastante lleno ahora mismo.)"

msgctxt "1456_Player"
msgid "Sorry, something came up."
msgstr "Lo siento, me ha surgido algo."

msgctxt "1468_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Is that so? Well, I hope you actually order something next time!"
msgstr "Is that so? Well, I hope you actually order something next time!"

msgctxt "1480_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Hey, thanks for always comin' to eat here. We're getting more customers than before, but y'know..."
msgstr "Hey, thanks for always comin' to eat here. We're getting more customers than before, but y'know..."

msgctxt "1492_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Lots of people can get how good our ramen is by eating it, but some people hate the strong smell in here so much, they won't even try it!"
msgstr "Lots of people can get how good our ramen is by eating it, but some people hate the strong smell in here so much, they won't even try it!"

msgctxt "1504_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "It makes me so sad! If only they realized that smell meant we were making real, authentic Kyushu ramen in here!"
msgstr "It makes me so sad! If only they realized that smell meant we were making real, authentic Kyushu ramen in here!"

msgctxt "1516_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "I wish someone'd tell everyone that handy little fact. Get us some word-of-mouth advertising to get our ramen into mouths, you know?"
msgstr "I wish someone'd tell everyone that handy little fact. Get us some word-of-mouth advertising to get our ramen into mouths, you know?"

msgctxt "1528_Player"
msgid "I see."
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "1540_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "We make our rich soup by boiling down pork bones until they break down into the broth. Those bones are full of collagen, which is super good for your skin."
msgstr "We make our rich soup by boiling down pork bones until they break down into the broth. Those bones are full of collagen, which is super good for your skin."

msgctxt "1552_Owner of Kyushu No. 1 Star"
msgid "Normally, ladies are super into collagen-related stuff. Guess the smell is that much of a turnoff..."
msgstr "Normally, ladies are super into collagen-related stuff. Guess the smell is that much of a turnoff..."

msgctxt "1564_Player"
msgid "(Ramen chock full of collagen... Bet the girls at the hostess club would want to know about this.)"
msgstr "(Ramen chock full of collagen... Bet the girls at the hostess club would want to know about this.)"

